data.title: Pau Gasol Memphis Grizzlies NBA McFarlane action figure NIB Grizz new in box
data.meta_description: Up for sale is a Pau Gasol Memphis Grizzlies Series 3 McFarlane action figure. This Pau Gasol Memphis Grizzlies action figure comes new in original packaging and is an officially licensed NBA product. Pau Gasol was the 3rd overall pick in the 2001 NBA Draft by the Atlanta Hawks who then traded him to the Memphis Grizzlies for Sharif Abdur-Rahim. Pau Gasol played for the Memphis Grizzlies from 2001-2008 winning the 2002 NBA Rookie of the Year and making the 2006 NBA All-Star Team. ---The Pau Gasol Memphis Grizzlies McFarlane action figure can be yours for 39.
